<item>
            <title>[LU-7467] Quota Account wrong</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7467</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Quota reporting zero inode usage for user.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;root.pfe21 # lfs quota -u mcantiel /nobackupp8
Disk quotas &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; user mcantiel (uid 30403):
     Filesystem  kbytes   quota   limit   grace   files   quota   limit   grace
     /nobackupp8 59604412  530000000 1100000000       -       0  100000  150000       
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But user has &amp;gt;74K files&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;root.pfe21 # find /nobackupp8/yjiang2/StarMidMHD3 -user mcantiel 2&amp;gt;/dev/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; | wc -l
74223
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example file &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
